<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idab5f3514-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5" identifier="/us/usc/t10/s9061"><num value="9061">§ 9061.</num><heading> Regulations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The President may prescribe regulations for the government of the Air Force.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idab5f3515-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5">(<ref href="/us/act/1956-08-10/ch1041">Aug. 10, 1956, ch. 1041</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/70A/493">70A Stat. 493</ref>, § 8061; renumbered § 9061, <ref href="/us/pl/115/232/dA/tVIII/s806/c">Pub. L. 115–232, div. A, title VIII, § 806(c)</ref>, <date date="2018-08-13">Aug. 13, 2018</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/132/1833">132 Stat. 1833</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
